default2. Introduction to Enterprise Rent-A-Cardefault&#xa0;defaultEnterprise Rent-A-Car was founded in 1957 and is an industry leading, multi-national company with approximately one million vehicles in its global rental fleet and an 
defaultannual turnover of more than $16.4
